<head>EAR</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">耳朵</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">耳</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>ORGAN of HEARING.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current standard word for the ear is ěr 耳.</p>
<p>2. Guó 聝 is a rare word referring to the ear cut off dead soldiers in war.</p>
        </div>
